Thomas Craig Roberts, Jr.

Age : 74Public asset : 763,840 USDLinked companies :  EZCORP Inc 





Summary 



Mr. Thomas C. Roberts, Jr., is on the Board of Directors at EZCORP, Inc. Mr. Roberts was previously employed as a Lead Independent Director by Albemarle & Bond Holdings Plc, Chairman by PENSCO Trust Co., Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by Kitsune Corp., Chairman by Pensco, Inc., President by Computer Systems Co., Inc., President & Director by Control Data Corp., Chief Executive Officer by Fairchild Camera & Instrument Corp., and Chief Financial Officer & Executive Director by Schlumberger NV.He received his undergraduate degree from US Military Academy.



